definitions.definition: The practice of incising a design onto a hard, flat surface, by cutting grooves into it.
The art of producing an image from an engraved printing form , typically made of copper .
A print produced from an engraving.
The art of drawing music notation at high quality, particularly on a computer.

main_definition: ( art ) The practice of incising a design onto a hard, flat surface, by cutting grooves into it.
secondary_definitions: ( printing ) The art of producing an image from an engraved printing form , typically made of copper .
( countable ) A print produced from an engraving.
( music ) The art of drawing music notation at high quality, particularly on a computer.
